description:
Spice up your FUSER™ outfit with this Look Pack which contains:
Baggy Pants (Color Palette, Meaty, Manta), Cold Weather Jacket (Color Palette, Grimy, Digital), Construction Boots (Color Palette), Flight Instructor Glasses (Color Palette), Bucket Hat (Heart, Red Handed)
Requires FUSER™ base game to play.
name: Premium Look Pack: Streetwear
